Class ConsoleImpl

java.lang.Object
cat.uvic.teknos.dam.kamika.model.impl.ConsoleImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Console
public class ConsoleImpl extends Object implements Console
Concrete implementation of the Console interface. Represents a video game console with its main attributes.

Related tables: - Many-to-many relationship with Game.
